{"tid":199342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"父母係水上人，純粹想呻吓","createTime":"2017-04-13T06:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T06:40:05.000Z","uid":101650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4eb507066f42cec5ba74de96e35c652359c8ce0","tid":199342,"uid":101650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:24:27.000Z","msg":"[利申左先: 唔食魚]<br />\n從細到大，屋企永遠每餐最少會有一味魚整既餸，小學生嗰陣總係會逼我食少少，一食就想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到上左中學，已經唔會逼我食，但間唔中有一味係咸魚炒xx，仲要聲稱唔係魚嚟(一聞就知係咸魚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)。電飯煲煮飯嗰陣加左碟魚入去，嘩屌成碗飯都係魚味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n魚煲出嚟既湯都係好有味，聞到都唔想飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屋企人平時又會用魚湯做湯底整麵，一邊食一邊想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知 其實好折墮 但 我真係頂唔順啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a048f2e66ce4c2737352e2394876bba82a908ae","tid":199342,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:26:06.000Z","msg":"跪低求你屋企人唔好逼你食魚啦"},{"pid":"b0372b8f046a16bf5c1def37f2b5dfccc35780f1","tid":199342,"uid":26038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:28:22.000Z","msg":"電飯煲整魚係貪方便 分開蒸唔好慳果少少電費 最多叫條仆街仔俾多啲家用<br />\n魚湯難飲係太腥唔香 要落多啲薑"},{"pid":"44cfcd60f36e5bef0f4f03bd48ba2077f945ea83","tid":199342,"uid":21102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"魚湯好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}